  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<ul><li>Managing the development and sale of Divine Artisan's Bakery Products and service offerings on various e-commerce sites, sales platforms, delivery platforms by efficiently responding to customer's enquiries, processing orders and coordination to ensure the successful fulfillment of customer's orders.</li><li>Produce content and update Divine Artisan's social media platforms consistently to portray consistent brand image to achieve sales conversions. Implement marketing plans (organic/paid) to continuously increase Divine Artisan's online brand presence and awareness.</li><li>Management of Divine Artisan research & development & boost sales for business unit.</li><li>Establish & maintain rapport with customers and any assistance they may require.</li><li>Oversee and source bakery packaging & ingredients for new product developments.</li><li>Plan and coordinate the smooth execution of Divine Artisan's event services (Dessert Tables, Live Stations, Weddings etc.). </li><li>Solid knowledge & understanding of bakery's capabilities and implement strategies to increase efficiency, workflow and productivity of bakery operations.</li><li>Propose ideas for improvement of existing services and come up with proposals.</li></ul>",
